=== {{t3verb }} ===
'''為る''' ([[する]], [[suru]]) <!-- what does this mean?: (s irregular conjugation; サ行変格活用) -->

# To [[do]]. 
#* 何をしていますか。 (なにをしていますか。, nani o '''shite'''imasuka?, ''What are you '''doing'''?'')
# To [[wear]].
#* ネクタイを'''する''' (nekutai o '''suru''', ''to '''wear''' a tie'')


It's most common use is after a noun that can be done to indicate that the noun is being done, for example [[旅行]]する (ryok&#333; suru), to travel.

